<!-- PROJECT -->
<section id="projects">
<div class="container">
<h2 class="text-center mb-4">Featured Project</h2>

<div class="card p-4 small-card">
<h4 class="text-danger">
Sign Language Recognition using Flask & NLP
</h4>

<p>
<b>Sign Language</b> is a visual language that uses hand gestures,  
finger movements, and facial expressions to communicate,  
mainly used by hearing-impaired individuals.
</p>

<p>
This project recognizes hand gestures and converts them into readable text  
to bridge the communication gap between hearing-impaired users  
and the digital world.
</p>

<h6 class="mt-3">Technologies Used & Purpose</h6>
<ul>
<li><b>Python:</b> Core programming language used for gesture recognition logic.</li>
<li><b>OpenCV:</b> Captures and processes real-time hand gesture images.</li>
<li><b>NLP:</b> Converts recognized gestures into meaningful text.</li>
<li><b>Flask:</b> Connects backend processing with a simple web interface.</li>
</ul>

<div class="mt-2">
<span class="tech-badge">Python</span>
<span class="tech-badge">OpenCV</span>
<span class="tech-badge">NLP</span>
<span class="tech-badge">Flask</span>
</div>
</div>

</div>
</section>

